1. Molim vas, *donesite* mi čašu vode. (Please *bring* me a glass of water.)
2. Da li biste mogli da *donesete* ove knjige do kancelarije? (Could you *bring* these books to the office?)
3. Jelena će nam *doneseti* tortu za rođendan. (Jelena will *bring* us a cake for the birthday.)
4. Ako mi *donesete* novac, moći ću da platim račune. (If you *bring* me the money, I'll be able to pay the bills.)
5. Kad budete prolazili pored prodavnice, *donesite* mi hleb i mleko. (When you pass by the store, *bring* me bread and milk.)
6. Nije potrebno da mi *donesite* dokumente, samo ih skenirajte i pošaljite mi na mejl. (You don't need to *bring* me the documents, just scan them and send them to me by email.)
7. Gospodin Petrović je naručio picu, *donesite* mu je na stol. (Mr. Petrović ordered a pizza, *bring* it to his table.)
8. Ako *donesete* svoj laptop, možemo da radimo zajedno na projektu. (If you *bring* your laptop, we can work together on the project.)
9. Mama je rekla da mi *donesete* jaknu jer je napolju hladno. (Mom said to *bring* me my jacket because it's cold outside.)
10. Da li bi mogli da mi *donesete* čašu mleka i keks? (Could you *bring* me a glass of milk and some cookies?)